<emphasis id="ED90588C9A9AC06A3DA2D10EB7104ABE" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">m</emphasis>
stained in lactophenol cotton blue). Scale bars: 50 
<normalizedToken id="7416ED2EA7EE62BE41E2F79425008D4E" originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
(
<emphasis id="8B138355A5B410811EDCE40BC502A5BC" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">c, e</emphasis>
); 5 
